  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>Zero MsalAuthProvider.ts files remain in the repository outside of node_modules (verified by find command).</criterion>
    <criterion>A minimum of 2,321 lines of dead code are removed (4 file deletions x ~775 lines average).</criterion>
    <criterion>createLogger(prefix) factory function exists in src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/utils/logger.ts and is exported from the package barrel.</criterion>
    <criterion>createLogger returns an object with logInfo, logWarn, logError, and logDebug methods using the format [Spaarke.{prefix}] [{component}] {message}.</criterion>
    <criterion>logInfo, logWarn, and logDebug are guarded behind process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development'. logError always logs.</criterion>
    <criterion>All 10 listed top offender files have been migrated from raw console.log to the shared logger.</criterion>
    <criterion>PCF build (npm run build in src/client/pcf) passes with zero errors after all changes.</criterion>
